

=Bio=

Open Data evangelist at [[Open Knowledge Foundation]], Chairman of the German Chapter of the Open Knowledge Foundation, Project Coordinator for the [[Open Definition]], Coordinator of the Open Government Data Working Group. Former editor of the ePSIplatform.eu and Research Associate in the Department of Internet and Society at the Technical University in Berlin. Author of several studies and papers on the topics of Open Government, Open Data, Transparency and Participation. 


